          "sequence": 3,
          "status": "proposed",
          "timestamp": "2025-11-12T19:00:00Z",
          "decision_drivers": [
            "Efficiency: Content-addressed storage enables deduplication",
            "Performance: LRU cache for hot chunk sets",
            "GC: Easy to expire large sets without rewriting manifests",
            "Scalability: Supports large chunk sets without bloating manifests",
            "Implementation: Add CAS methods to ReceiptStore, implement CAS backend with path /.nr/cas/aa/bb/<sha256>.cbor, LRU cache (1-5 GB), reference counting, GC policy",
